proof:
Proof.
  arewrite sc in ecco by autoclass.
  apply init_c11_consistent.
  (* Prove both the P1 and P2 relation exists in the set
     * of actual executions of xy and the subgraphs of xy *)
  exists (fun r => exists r1 r2, psc⁺ ⊆ r1 ∪ r2 ∧ r = dom psc r1 ∪ r2)
    as ys.
  assert (psc = ∅₂).
  { rewrite <- domA. cset_ind_right.
    rewrite <- C_EXT_helper2.
    eapply c_ext_consistentbyandcountable and_comm.
    eapply and_assoc in IPC. simpl in IPC.
    tauto. des; eauto.
    splits. exists (@set_full G) (@set_of_nat G (countable_fin G)).
    split; eauto.
Qed.
